  "markup": "\u003Cp\u003EWe support you in fulfilling your civic duty as a juror. If you are summoned for jury duty, we will provide time off in accordance with applicable federal and state laws. This policy outlines the notification procedures you should follow, the documentation required, and information regarding compensation during your jury service. We recognize the importance of this civic responsibility and aim to minimize any financial hardship or work-related stress during this time.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u0026nbsp;\u003C/p\u003E"
}]]></Value>
